// Search any package → see: minified + gzipped size, download time

// Common size comparison:
// moment: 67.9 KB → date-fns: 2.4 KB per function
// lodash: 24.5 KB → you can tree-shake specific functions
// axios: 11.9 KB → fetch: 0 KB (built-in!)
// uuid: 1.2 KB → crypto.randomUUID(): 0 KB (built-in!)
// classnames: 0.4 KB → clsx: 0.3 KB (smaller alternative)

// Rule: check bundlephobia BEFORE every npm install
